race.description: Rohrs Home Timber And Hardware C1 Handicap
race.comment: INVINCIBLE PHANTOM (3) has returned in good order this campaign. Won his maiden first-up over 1000m at this track then finished second over 900m at Gunnedah last time. Has the gate speed to take up a forward position. Should prove too good for these. SWEDISH GLITTER (6) was a determined maiden winner last time out, scoring by a long neck over 900m at Wellington. Winning rider Zoe Hunt stays aboard, and she is one of the main chances. RUSSIAN EMBER (5) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 900m at Wellington, beaten 3.5 lengths into fourth. Goes up a rung or two but she is good enough to take this out. BRUMMAGEN (1) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better when third over 900m at Muswellbrook. Capable of featuring prominently.
